title: Seifuku de Vanilla Kiss
original_name: 制服でヴァニラ・キス
sinopse:
The moody, picturesque him. The puppy-like me who wants to express my love. I wonder if we can grasp this love well.

(Source: Chibi Manga)

Volume 6: Oyasumi no Chuu wa Kuchibiru ni Shite., Spicy Boy☆, Ani ni Aisaresugite Komattemasu Bangai-hen
